o1$ in the high temperature\nphase, is computed for large $N$. Remarkably, this is related to the number of\nlabeled Eulerian digraphs with $N$ nodes. Systematic methods to extend our\nresults to higher orders in $1/N$ are described.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Aug 2017 18:10:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 26 Sep 2019 20:10:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-30"}
