 an X-ray surface brightness profile we\nalso detect a possible density jump of $R=1.39^{+0.34}_{-0.22}$ co-located with\nthe newly discovered SE relic. This density jump would correspond to a shock\nfront Mach number of $\\mathcal{M}=1.26^{+0.25}_{-0.15}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Aug 2017 19:55:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-23"}
