t) presents the model and main results,\ndiscusses some applications and sketches the main ideas of the proof. The\nsecond part (supplementary informations) is much more detailed and provides\nmore examples as well as all the proofs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Aug 2017 21:53:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 3 Nov 2017 19:17:17 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 1 Nov 2018 12:05:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-01"}
